songs.title: Tulips In The Field*
songs.lyrics:
From snippet

..tonight
So come on baby, come on dive in

[Chorus]
We'll go dancin' in the breeze
We're dancin' in the breeze
Magic flowin' through my hair
My hair
We'll go burnin' through the skies
We're burnin' through the sky
Colors burstin' everywhere
You know that we're just like
Tulips in the field
Tulips in the field...
